{"tid":1438296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑警虐畜］黃大仙燒衣，警犬出真警犬。","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:48:54.000Z","uid":296193,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6b34bf992c4e1961ff584c25263e6c5ba6e561","tid":1438296,"uid":296193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0FMs36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0FMs36.jpg&h=9d1ccb7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月9日 黃大仙祈福除惡晚會，警察派出真警犬對付人群。期間警犬不斷嘗試撲向記者及群眾，警員以狗帶約束，並任由警犬對示威者踐吠叫。<br />\n<br />\n狗嗅覺比人靈敏百倍, 若吸入摧淚彈或胡椒噴霧對身體影響比人體嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n受過訓練的狗隻會服從主人命令，若警員放手讓牠追咬人群，一咬就住不會放口，而其他人一定幫手。但因為人平定唔夠狗隻大力，冇得選擇之下，可能會打暈狗隻。<br />\n<br />\n警員以狗隻控制人群，此舉無疑漠視動物安危。"},{"pid":"5f4d8158ef06cf504782cbbcd806632618618b53","tid":1438296,"uid":296193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"現場有記者投訴警員未有妥善控制狗隻，曾數度碰倒行家，令行家感到驚慌。"},{"pid":"e5f81d3da19c25d2e44994f01c1d3f304af82290","tid":1438296,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26aa2be206b58c261f173f6cf0bc428510df0556","tid":1438296,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8e83c9fec9dfa96880e1aeaa11eddf4f7ec302","tid":1438296,"uid":294711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"哈哈, 警犬唔係普通狗."},{"pid":"1d643738ea9c3b3503387516289b4a25f70f1776","tid":1438296,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}